<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Best Chest Calisthenics Workout Routine</h2>



<p>If you’re ready to get started increasing your chest strength and muscle size, use this sample workout routine. It is catered to a rep and set scheme that <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7927075/#:~:text=A%20high%20repetition%20scheme%20with%20light%20loads%20(15%2B%20repetitions%20per%20set%20with%20loads%20below%2060%25%20of%201RM)%20optimizes%20local%20muscular%20endurance%20improvements." target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">supports hypertrophy</a> to stimulate muscle mass progress.</p>



